6334","replies":90,"created_ts":1686039469,"created":"16:17:49","title":"生娃还是需要冷静点想一想","author":"mie","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mie","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9924/3aab/74159_mini.png?m=1422427664"},{"id":946104,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"展示的功能像是 AR+VR<br />展示的现实空间，是通过摄像头传递到眼睛里的？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946104","replies":89,"created_ts":1685990533,"created":"02:42:13","title":"Apple Vision Pro 讨论贴","author":"zhangsimon","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zhangsimon","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a701/01b2/10655_mini.png?m=1685005792"},{"id":946144,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>1500 换 8g 含泪赚 80%</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946144","replies":81,"created_ts":1686015136,"created":"09:32:16","title":"库克的内存和存储还是那么抠，可吐了","author":"polobug","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/polobug","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ae4fb893fd58e8514dfd21a52cce6d3f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":946126,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>M2 版本的 Air</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946126","replies":81,"created_ts":1686012547,"created":"08:49:07","title":"MacBook Air 新 15 寸怎么样，值得入手吗？","author":"BeforeTooLate","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/BeforeTooLate","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0dae/9391/455039_mini.png?m=1667288533"},{"id":946092,"node":"NAS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/nas","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3cef/96dc/949_mini.png?m=1614702882","description":"<p>去年双十一，500 多元在 JD 自营店买的 TiPlus 5000 1TB ，一直放在 NAS 内使用。半年多就 0E 了。</p>\n<p>昨天晚上发现 NAS 上的虚拟机无法启动，检查了一下是硬盘镜像损坏了；再一查 smart ，发现有 0E 。</p>\n<p>发现后赶紧把固态全盘备份了一下，然后 0E 瞬间暴涨到 23 ，有四个文件完全损毁，好在盘里没有任何重要数据。</p>\n<p>已经不敢再用了，准备售后吧。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>之前也是考虑到三星有 0E 健康度问题，西数有冷数据问题，同时支持国产所以买了致钛。为了保证原厂品质，特地没有选梵想之类更便宜的...</p>\n<p>谁知道半年就出了问题。现在还有靠谱的固态吗，经不起折腾，太累了...</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/18HF4W1.png\"/>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SwNHG8P.png\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946092","replies":74,"created_ts":1685982424,"created":"00:27:04","title":"致钛 TiPlus 5000 数据丢失， 0E 暴涨","author":"mikewang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/mikewang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/b728/8030/81681_mini.png?m=1683726911"},{"id":946197,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181","description":"<p>按照我的身高体重选择的合适的尺码，除了裤腿，其他都合适，裤腿总是长一截。\n如果买小一号，裤腿合适了，其他地方又不合适了，比如裆部又有点紧了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946197","replies":69,"created_ts":1686021038,"created":"11:10:38","title":"为什么裤子的裤腿设计要那么长啊？","author":"thinkm","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/thinkm","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2d989f5d2e94bce12f361acc26845297?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":946282,"node":"信息安全","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/security","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4f2/3670/260_mini.png?m=1650095354","description":"<p>被如下钓鱼网站骗了 200RMB.好气，怎么能处理掉呢？\n官方：<a href=\"http://www.toshiba.com.cn\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.toshiba.com.cn</a>\n和\n钓鱼站：<a href=\"http://toshlba.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">toshlba.com</a></p>\n<p>请大佬们指导指导。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946282","replies":66,"created_ts":1686032124,"created":"14:15:24","title":"钓鱼网站，怎么处理","author":"justdoitzZ","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/justdoitzZ","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b586ab88b3b351d4b89defa266ddc282?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":946356,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","description":"<p>楼主现在 26 ，是个 5 年经验的 Android 客户端开发，无时无刻不在想着这个问题，有点迷茫，想请教一下大家。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946356","replies":63,"created_ts":1686043552,"created":"17:25:52","title":"2023 年及以后， Android 开发的出路在哪里？","author":"silencelixing","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/silencelixing","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6b5bb02bdd362e602c1bc4e68aaffa5f?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":946182,"node":"分享发现","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1650127281","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/kaDQPpU.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kaDQPpU.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />-----------------------------------------------<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gr4ndtV.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gr4ndtV.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />-----------------------------------------------<br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/7A3XRyi.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7A3XRyi.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a><br /><br />-----------------------------------------------<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://blog.hzao.top/2023/05/27/bupt-heyteaevent/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://blog.hzao.top/2023/05/27/bupt-heyteaevent/</a><br />感谢这些“较真”的人，让这个社会变的美好了一点点。至少北邮不会再有人敢偷外卖了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/946182","replies":62,"created_ts":1686019395,"created":"10:43:15","title":"北邮偷外卖事件，出后续了","author":"oppoic","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oppoic","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5bc5/513b/176424_mini.png?m=1670912786"},{"id":946243,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https: